{"tid":852931,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【C朗涉姦】司機做證：個女仔事後笑呵呵","createTime":"2018-10-08T08:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T15:35:00.000Z","uid":161311,"like":346,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9a43a60fe1c4171d0f4f4acf61ff33d227f59098","tid":852931,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙球星C朗被前女模特兒Kathryn Mayorga指控喺2009年強姦佢，近日被美國警方翻舊帳，搞到周身蟻，面臨身敗名裂。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，有1位名為Vince Humphrey的士司機出來為C朗辯護，話2005年同樣有位英國女人指控C朗強姦，但當時佢喺酒店接載當事人時，女方滿面笑容，仲大讚C朗可愛，過幾日就告C朗強姦，所以佢相信C朗今次都係被老屈。 <br />\n<br />\nVince Humphrey話：「個女人上車之後好興奮，仲笑呵呵讚C朗可愛，身體肌肉完美到令人難以置信，佢仲同我講已經為自己同C朗將來嘅囝囝改好名，估唔到過幾日睇新聞，話C朗強姦佢。」 <br />\n<br />\n當年C朗被英國警方盤問9個鐘之後，撤銷控罪，Vince Humphrey認為C朗今次都會大步檻過。"},{"pid":"fea0052e6d3bacf1167b8712157d1e2278a38b44","tid":852931,"uid":76399,"like":248,"dislike":1,"score":247,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"有得屈一大筆，比我都笑呵呵啦"},{"pid":"4921b8b532267bb92874e995fe622f7788759924","tid":852931,"uid":198866,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"原文？標題同內容差咁遠"},{"pid":"755143a2ef905e2beaaa7da31c7f87f63cd2acea","tid":852931,"uid":84834,"like":48,"dislike":5,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:40:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲post唔會推到2頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58423b5f8e084bdc3b5fe32b7652d6c7c87c90d3","tid":852931,"uid":150400,"like":10,"dislike":26,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"931aa62cfcab3ec3070adfbfc622a4b08f628525","tid":852931,"uid":35176,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"乜原來屌屎忽會生仔 同直腸朗對好口供先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407bf33965f87e9b8867e83d3bc0a64a1e4d48d5","tid":852931,"uid":34852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:33: